item_name.value: Tylenol Acetaminophen 650mg Extended Release Caplets, 8 Hour Arthritis Pain Relief, Joint Pain Reliever, Fever Reducer, Fast & Long-Lasting Relief, Oral Medicine for Minor Aches, 225 Count

directions.value: Do not take more than directed (see overdose warning) Adults Take 2 caplets every 8 hours with water Swallow whole; do not crush, chew, split or dissolve Do not take more than 6 caplets in 24 hours Do not use for more than 10 days unless directed by a doctor Under 18 years of age Ask a doctor Other Information Store between 20-25oC (68-77oF) Do not use if carton is opened. Do not use if foil inner seal imprinted with "TYLENOL" is broken or missing Questions or comments? call 1-877-895-3665 (toll-free) or 215-273-8755 (collect)

model_name.value: 8 Hour Arthritis Pain Relief Extended-Release Tablets 650 mg Acetaminophen

ingredients.value: Active Ingredient (in each caplet) Acetaminophen 650 mg Purpose Pain reliever/fever reducer Inactive Ingredients Carnauba wax, hydroxyethyl cellulose, hypromellose, magnesium stearate, microcrystalline cellulose, modified starch, povidone, powdered cellulose, pregelatinized starch, sodium starch glycolate, titanium dioxide, triacetin

bullet_point.value: Fast & continuous arthritis pain relief: Extended-release caplets with bi-layer design deliver an immediate-release first layer for rapid 650mg acetaminophen action and a sustained second layer for up to 8 hours overnight comfort.

Powerful 650mg acetaminophen extended release: Each bi-layer caplet delivers proven pain relief and fever reduction to temporarily ease minor aches and pains due to arthritis, backache, headache, toothache, common cold, and menstrual cramps.

Stomach-friendly non-aspirin formula: Tylenol caplets contain no NSAIDs and are gentle on your stomach while providing effective relief; OTC brand for safe arthritis and joint pain control when used as directed.

Broad spectrum arthritis and pain relief: Adults 18+ can use one caplet to temporarily ease joint pain in hands, wrists, knees, ankles, elbows, and feet, as well as backache, headache, toothache, menstrual cramps, and cold symptoms.

Dosage & safety guidelines: Take one caplet every 8 hours as needed; do not exceed four caplets in 24 hours. Consult a healthcare professional if pain persists more than two days, or before use if on blood thinners or other medications.

safety_warning.value: Liver warning: This product contains acetaminophen. Severe liver damage may occur if you take More than 6 caplets in 24 hours, which is the maximum daily amount With other drugs containing acetaminophen 3 or more alcoholic drinks every day while using this product Allergy alert: acetaminophen may cause severe skin reactions. Symptoms may include: Skin reddening Blisters Rash If a skin reaction occurs, stop use and seek medical help right away. Do not use With any other drug containing acetaminophen (prescription or nonprescription). If you are not sure whether a drug contains acetaminophen, ask a doctor or pharmacist. If you are allergic to acetaminophen or any of the inactive ingredients in this product Ask a doctor before use if you have liver disease Ask a doctor or pharmacist before use if you are taking the blood thinning drug warfarin Stop use and ask a doctor if Pain gets worse or lasts more than 10 days Fever gets worse or last more than 3 days New symptoms occur Redness or swelling is present These could be signs of a serious condition. If pregnant or breast-feeding, ask a health professional before use. Keep out of reach of children. Overdose warning: In case of overdose, get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center right away. (1-800-222-1222) Quick medical attention is critical for adults as well as for children even if you do not notice any signs or symptoms.

Product Profile.product_summary: Tylenol 8HR Arthritis Pain is an over-the-counter acetaminophen medication in extended-release caplet form, designed to provide up to 8 hours of relief from arthritis pain and minor aches. Each bottle contains 225 caplets, each with 650 mg of acetaminophen, suitable for adult use.

title.text: Tylenol Arthritis Pain Medication Caplets, Acetaminophen 650 mg, Extended-Release Formula, 225 Count Bottle for Adults, Aspirin-Free

bullets.text: Experience up to 8 hours of arthritis pain relief with each medication extended release pain medication caplet, designed to help reduce the need for frequent dosing. The pain extended release formula gradually delivers acetaminophen, supporting sustained comfort so you can focus on daily activities without constant interruptions.

Formulated specifically for arthritis and joint pain, this caplet targets discomfort in the hands, knees, and other sensitive joints. The specialized blend aims to address minor aches associated with arthritis, offering a tailored solution for adults seeking joint care support.

Easy-to-swallow caplet design helps those with swallowing difficulties take their pain relief with confidence. The smooth, compact shape is intended to promote comfortable ingestion, making it suitable for adults who prefer a tablet that is gentle to take.

Gentle on the stomach, this acetaminophen-based formula contains no aspirin, providing an option for individuals with sensitivities or digestive concerns. The caplets are designed to minimize stomach discomfort, making them ideal for regular use by those cautious about gastrointestinal effects.

Suitable for long-term use, this pain reliever offers a reassuring choice for seniors and adults managing chronic arthritis. The extended-release formula and straightforward dosing instructions support ongoing comfort, helping users maintain their daily routines with peace of mind.

description.text:
Experience convenient support for joint comfort with this medication extended release pain medication, designed specifically for adults seeking relief from arthritis discomfort and minor aches. The medication adult pain reliever features an advanced formula that gradually delivers its benefits, allowing you to manage soreness in your hands, knees, and other joints with fewer interruptions to your daily routine.

Each bottle offers an ample supply of swallow caplets, making it easy for adults to integrate into their daily wellness regimen. The active ingredient: acetaminophen 650 mg per caplet medication, is recognized for being gentle on the stomach and free from aspirin, making it a suitable choice for individuals with sensitivities or digestive considerations. The caplet design is smooth and compact, providing a comfortable option for those who sometimes struggle with swallowing larger pills.

These pain pills that relieve joint discomfort are tailored for ongoing use. The extended release mechanism is ideal for those who need sustained comfort throughout the day or night, and also serves as an effective acetaminophen medication for sleep when occasional aches disrupt rest.
